{"tid":2253783,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"【網速問題】Modem直出有1000，Router得10MB","createTime":"2020-10-22T11:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T02:24:20.000Z","uid":7955,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c0ff074e0272243746730ea593c82a014142415a","tid":2253783,"uid":7955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T11:40:39.000Z","msg":"大家好，我個情況有啲詭異，希望咁多位有識之士幫幫手　<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家Router用緊ASUS AX56U，同網上行1,000mb Plan，電話用到WiFi，上到網嘅。OFCA Speedtest iPhone 11有 3xx mbps(dl)同4xx mbps(ul)左右。<br />\n<br />\n但係電腦經LAN線就有問題啦，張LAN卡除咗一開始出到1,000mbps：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/spkTe0M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FspkTe0M.jpg&h=4384e0b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就長期處於10mbps嘅速度，而且個網絡狀態唔係「沒有網絡連線」或者「已拔除」：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TzGyZuo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTzGyZuo.jpg&h=37effaf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SbZ8OnK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSbZ8OnK.jpg&h=ab79f51f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請教大家到底係邊度出咗問題，可以點解決　<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf9259b3b4da334ad9879508c3da32bc3555ce5","tid":2253783,"uid":56107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T11:46:07.000Z","msg":"即係駁完線之後OK，隔一陣先出問題？<br />\n定係電腦駁Router就唔work"},{"pid":"4a3ba84fa9dd85838fbf1932c15cf4de644cda94","tid":2253783,"uid":15055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T11:48:26.000Z","msg":"冇IP ADDRESS 既"},{"pid":"e867840d50893ab3b2e1d516be15d0f56ed80b45","tid":2253783,"uid":7955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daf9259b3b4da334ad9879508c3da32bc3555ce5","tid":2253783,"uid":56107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T11:46:07.000Z","msg":"即係駁完線之後OK，隔一陣先出問題？<br />\n定係電腦駁Router就唔work